OBJECTIVE: destroy all alien EGGS.

 this sector contains 3 rooms infested with alien eggs. find
 and destroy them before exiting.



            ------------------------------------

PICKING UP AMMO: ammunition can be picked up in the same way
  as equipment. in this mission< your r.a.w>s start the game
 UNLOADED. you  will need to pick up some of the ammo strewn
 on the ground just north of your deployment point. 

USING SECURITY CONSOLE: in this sector< all the doors are
 locked. you must access the security console< to UNLOCK
 them. (there is a picture of the security console on the
 main options screen

            ------------------------------------
 once all the eggs are destroyed< EXIT via the blast door
 next to your deployment point.
            ------------------------------------



SECTOR INFORMATION:

 -    boxed area     :-             -  deployment point.   -
 -   yellow cross    :-             -  security console.   -
 -   yellow arrow    :-             -  exit door.          -
